#title[Building Paiagram]

It is relatively easy to build Paiagram.

= Linux

I honestly have no idea how to build Paiagram on any Linux distribution.

= Nix/NixOS

Just download the fonts and enter the devshell then `cargo build`. Improvements are planned.

= Windows

Just download the fonts then `cargo build`

= MacOS

I do not know the exact procedure but I guess it is roughly the same idea.
